INSERT INTO `information` (`id`, `content`) VALUES (1,'<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">National Car Pass\r\nof Greece<o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">The mileage does not\r\nalways correspond to the actual number of kilometers driven. How can I check if\r\nthe mileage is logical? The Car pass manages this database with odometer\r\nreadings.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">The European Parliament\r\nis now busy to make law about car Kilometers and fraud. That means in the near\r\nfetched is fact that all car kilometer must be registered in the database.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">What is the Car pass?<o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Car pass stands for Kilometer\r\nPass for your car. This is a Greece national database that counteracts mileage\r\nfraud. From 2019 onwards, we collect in cooperation with the car dealers and private\r\nowners of the cars Kilometer registration of all cars in Greece. This database\r\nis now managed by Car pass. <o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">A Car pass report is\r\nan overview of the odometer readings in recent years. This report is also\r\ncalled Counter Report.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">All approved companies\r\nare required to register the odometer reading. This creates a reliable picture\r\nof the kilometer history of the cars you sell or buy.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Consult the counter\r\nreading by yourself<o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">You can check whether\r\nthe Kilometers is logical and request the counter report free of charge from\r\nthe Car pass website before purchasing the car..<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">What do you need to\r\ncheck the car kilometers?<o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">You need the Car make,\r\nModel? Build year, Number plate, then you can see if the kilometer are Logical.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Registration:<o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">In order to consult\r\nthe Car pass you must register to access the car pass database.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Your personal or\r\ncompany information will be use only to access Car Pass database.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Without Registration\r\nyou can`t access the car pass database.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">After registration you\r\ncan search for car and print the report of the car kilometers, from first\r\nRegistration date of the car to the day you make the search.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Registration\r\ninformation:<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">We have two type of\r\nRegistrations.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">1- Normal user , you\r\ncan register and add your Vehicle Mileage.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">2- Dealer user, you\r\ncan Register Vehicle mileage of just read vehicle mileage.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">The price for user /\r\ndealer Registration or mileage registration is Free.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Mileage Check<o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Pay attention! With a\r\nmeter reading check you will not receive an overview of the odometer readings,\r\nbut only the judgment \"logical\", \"illogical\" or \"no\r\njudgment\".<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">You are a seller?<o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">As a seller you must\r\nprovide the buyer with a valid Car-Pass.<br>\r\nYou get Car pass when you register your vehicle on Carpass.gr. the registration\r\nis Free.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">You Buy a Vehicle?</span></b><span s